Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要打開電視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我想看龍華
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,副將戰  終局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三人都已迅速聽牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,將勝利果實交付大將手中的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會是哪所學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很像呢  鷺森選手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她和十年前與我交戰的赤土選手的打法很像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  赤土選手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正擔任阿知賀的教練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸  閒家700  莊家1300
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,副將戰結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,王者白糸台勉強保持著第一名的位置進入大將戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  手臂回轉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一直提到100檔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暖和起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,100什麼的  會為了這種荒謬數字高興的高中生只有小穩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是小學男生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣拿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千里山的江口夕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還記得她在濱名湖的樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士就快開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全記不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人平時也好採訪時也好  都是穿男生的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽的時候卻好好穿著校服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯…嗯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說  小穩也要穿上校服去比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:01.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,灼姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校服？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…這是跟憧借的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上這個就感覺自己是阿知賀的學生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從一開始就是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  希望你能加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後交給你了  阿知賀的大將
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我會大幹一場的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小灼  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了  部長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,努力了呢  灼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亦野學姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你幫我增加了不利因素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…還是一如既往不饒人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分數被削減成這樣  還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被狠狠擺了一道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狠狠地？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  如果連大星也輸掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我這一無是處的立場將會變得更危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  一定要贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來就是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不可能輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,清水谷學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從醫院直接去賽場了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.08,0:05:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,清水谷學姐是三年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,將會在高中聯賽的賽場上綻放光彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  她將會採取與二回戰不同的強攻打法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,園城寺學姐的事也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  半決賽第一場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於進入了大將賽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠進入決賽舞台的是這其中的兩所學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一切的可能都交付給這四個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九州的強豪  新道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,壓軸的是與白水哩齊名的雙ACE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能完成連攜嗎  鶴田姬子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,眾所周知的千里山女子的部長清水谷龍華
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平均手牌得分在關西是首屈一指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（平均手牌得分：只算手牌番數和符數所得到的分數，\N而不算本場、立直供托、流局不聽罰分之類的特殊分）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闊別10年的高中聯賽半決賽  阿知賀女子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天沒穿運動服哦  高鴨穩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,王者白糸台唯一的一年生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然出現的超新星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為宮永照的後繼者呼聲非常高的大星淡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到決戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇  真的好慘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,六向聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:16.95,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（六向聽：在手中的牌最少要換六張才能達至聽牌。日本麻將中\N最惡劣只會是七對子的六向聽，就如穩乃的手牌）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然出現了  五向聽的開局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了大星選手以外  配牌都很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每家都是五六向聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對龍華也有效  好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從預選賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大星選手的對手就一直有很大的幾率拿到難以和牌的配牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是幸好之後能普通地進張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.68,0:07:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們部裏能破解這個的也只有終局的堯深了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  在二回戰的時候新道寺破解了幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是淡在放水吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  差不多成型了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,5200
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有自己的配牌不錯真是太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,東二局  幸運的是我是莊家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看機會會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:24.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸  每人500
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快速和牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姬子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fsp54.545}　{\fsp1.818}Key{\r}\N滿貫鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滿貫來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩向聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然被破解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是集結了兩個人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能強於淡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人本來的實力也都很強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,12300
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第四巡的門前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的絕對安全圈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  挺能幹嘛  新道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,副將戰中因為沒有這個二本場就先暫且不論
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,3200
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來才是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,東三局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倍滿…來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赤土老師囑咐我要小心  東三局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦  我很期待倍滿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這副牌將成為倍滿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏這種時候坐莊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很期待倍滿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可也想試著阻止一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人開心得不得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白糸台的大星淡  確實很強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,二回戰的時候也是大鬧了一場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是以一年級生的身份當上白糸台大將的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我們的連攜也從來沒被阻止過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這份羈絆  如果你能打破的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這份積攢起來的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隻身一人的你  會有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒家4000  莊家8000
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是倍滿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被逆轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新道寺的那招  真強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要暫且先放棄防守呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,倍滿炸裂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一位的新道寺上升到了第二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,距離第一位也是觸手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,落到最後一位了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  憐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入學一個月就升格為白糸台最強隊伍的正式隊員的一年生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解她的不同尋常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後是新道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用雙ACE的陣容組合增強火力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才既然和了倍滿  後半的累計役滿應該也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能有點危險呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,龍華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果憐在這裏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能安心點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快想起來  龍華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,龍華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐  要不要我買些喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是喜歡膝枕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這一點可是確實真的有理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  能看到一巡之後的神奇能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果本來就很強的龍華能有這種力量不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能把力量傳給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  所以才用膝枕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用謝我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我冷靜地想了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得她在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然現在想起來也還是覺得在胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  龍華
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏  我能感受到憐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏也不是獨自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會讓你看見未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打出南？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是處理字牌也應該是先北風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從數據流上來說？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一望可知是全帶的配牌  而且有鳴牌的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保留字牌的話效率應該更高吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…棄兩萬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這時候不棄只剩一枚的北風嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是與之前不同風格的棄牌順序呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,清水谷龍華以其正確的棄牌順序和精準的讀牌技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在關西選手的平均手牌得分中位列前茅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一局…會發生些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,12000點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與看到的完全相符的和了牌形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:50.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這東四局我是在警戒著鶴姬能否和牌…怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\fsp305.455}　{\fsp1.818}Key{\r}\N這局沒拿到對應的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也不是感覺能和的配牌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,王者陷落！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:03.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從先鋒戰開始一直維持領先的白糸台  突然之間跌至末位！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四校的分數雖然看起來不相上下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是單看大將戰的話新道寺的分數是壓倒性的領先
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說按這樣發展下去  新道寺會升上首位？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕還能和一把大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟憐給我看到的一模一樣  也就是說必然會形成看到的樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「能見即能和」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是枕神小憐的神諭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與憐不同  我只能看見自己最後的和牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人的我就看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莊家…很想趁現在盡量和牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此  這南一局是白水哩和過牌的一局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然上一局也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但似乎有些本質上的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這一局…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有兩個人的連攜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒家3000  莊家6000
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新道寺跳滿自摸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一度跌落至三萬點深淵的新道寺竟竟竟然…升至第一！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全和小鍛治雀士的預想相符！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本最強連預測也是最強！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…真是短暫的首位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧  看到下一步了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鳴牌斷…分數會不會太少了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.29,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（鳴牌斷：以吃碰杠完成斷，此處如果沒有寶牌就只有1番30符）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是這一局的最佳形式哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說總能看到最佳形式嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是最佳形式  而是最高得點的和牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:18:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有別的和牌形式  能看到的道路也只此一條
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像越來越小了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可別搞錯看到的順序哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然憐都這麼說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:10.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,1000點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這兩個人為什麼能和這麼多牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…至少比和不了牌要好多了…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是來去匆匆啊  你就不能一直留在這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.42,0:18:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,龍華的大腿再怎麼豐滿  能存儲在那的小憐能量也是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概只能再來兩次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我再稍微胖一點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萬萬不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這回能看到滿貫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.69,0:19:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來可要謹遵用法用量  珍惜使用小憐的機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸  閒家2000  莊家4000
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩兩次嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…我才不管什麼關西最強什麼北九州最強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在我眼皮底下和了那麼多牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多忍耐到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以動手了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,淡認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遺憾  沒能保留到決賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在校內的練習比賽裏也沒見過幾次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說明對方是相當強勁的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雙立直？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:07.01,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（雙立直：指在第一巡時立直而之前不可以有任何的\N吃碰杠(包括暗杠)，比一般的立直多一番）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這可真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大星淡選手  雙立直！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在其它三家的手牌進展遲緩的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真是形成了鮮明對比
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是役種只有雙立而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是那樣就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在正式比賽裏這是第一次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  地區比賽中有過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,記得是在決賽大將戰後半的東場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當時的理由居然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想在綜合得分上輸給堯深嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,輸給照倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能把那局和現在這次聯繫起來的對手應該還不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有  淡也不會輸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩  你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大星淡同學的雙立…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是赤土老師說過的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩  要小心大星淡的雙立直哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雙立直？  為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大星淡是今年剛涌現的超新星  比賽記錄還很少
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  單憑能將他家的手牌進展變慢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得還不至於讓這個一年級生進入正選
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經足夠強了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…白糸台校內有很多支隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在互相之間的比賽中獲勝的隊伍才能出戰全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以代表白糸台參賽的並不一定是校內前五名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且每一支隊伍都有各自的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,宮永照的隊伍感覺上就是強化了攻擊性
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:41.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大星淡也是攻擊型的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說她一直以來都收斂著鋒銳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  為什麼偏偏要注意那牌譜裏只有一次的雙立直呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西東京大賽的配套設施非常完備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有專門跟蹤拍攝全部選手錶情的攝影視頻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是西東京地區松庵女學院的大將
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在地區決賽上和大星淡比賽時的錄像
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人很活躍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  這孩子個人戰的成績也相當厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看她差不多3秒之後的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是大星淡打出雙立直之前的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是立直的時候  也不是和牌的時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說感覺到了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以下只是我的推測了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.08,0:22:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大星淡雙立直之後有幾處要提防一下為好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杠！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對攻到底的話就要隨摸隨打
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在她杠牌之後  只能緊跟著棄完全安全牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.60,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（完全安全牌：完全不可能放銃的牌。這裏包括「淡打出來的牌」\N「淡立直之後所有人的捨牌」及「不能構成任何刻子，順子或對子的牌」）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.64,0:22:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…即使我現在是在終局的燒雞末位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在8索是障壁  和9索需要雙碰或單騎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.70,0:23:13.99,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（障壁：防守理論。指在場上四張一樣的牌，尤其指2378四種牌。\N如場上看到四張8索就不能構成帶9索的順子，而9索也只會輸對碰和單騎）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓莊家大星這麼連莊下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也沒安牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏姑且先聽牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:25.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逆翻轉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  只有雙立直兩番
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.06,0:23:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杠裏寶牌？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.44,0:23:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,18000點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直擊一萬八千！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白糸台重新奪回了王座！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.45,0:23:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對攻的話…之前的8筒就放銃了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟這個相似的和牌  之前有過一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.66,0:24:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.29,0:24:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:04.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確定了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.25,0:24:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可還沒打算下莊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.43,0:24:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又來雙立直！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.93,0:24:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次雙立直了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的役種依然只有雙立直呢…暫時看來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.61,0:24:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊配牌五向聽  莊家倒是接連雙立直
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.86,0:24:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是憐只能再召喚兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.45,0:24:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話我想把機會留到後半坐莊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.95,0:24:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒有鑰匙  我也要靠自己的力量流掉這局！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.25,0:24:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骰子轉出的數字是多少來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.59,0:24:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…看起來應該是右2
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.59,0:24:51.76,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（右2：指骰子為2時，右方的下家餘下2墩牌開始摸牌。正式來說\N包括有右2、6、10，對(對家)3、7、11，左(上家)4、8、12和(自家)5、9）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.38,0:24:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雙一？  漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.97,0:24:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩是否有與大星淡一戰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.85,0:25:00.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就看這局的了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.93,0:25:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杠
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.14,0:25:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我的預測是正確的話  數巡之內大星淡就能和牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.32,0:25:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.69,0:25:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事也沒發生就到了第16巡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.20,0:25:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.57,0:25:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  預測也會有偏差的時候嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.57,0:25:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟大星淡的數據太少
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.24,0:25:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.46,0:25:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這牌…有些詭異…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.88,0:25:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.13,0:25:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.97,0:25:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,7700點的一本場是…  8000點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.72,0:25:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿知賀女子！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.18,0:25:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…叫什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.06,0:25:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.77,0:25:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人就是阿知賀女子的大將？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.86,0:25:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.36,0:25:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高鴨穩乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.03,0:25:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前半戰結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.12,0:26:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿知賀女子  高鴨穩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.24,0:26:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直擊首位  結束了燒雞的局面！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.83,0:26:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半決賽第一回合  剩下的只有大將戰後半戰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.46,0:26:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛那局是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.04,0:26:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙身上有什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.80,0:26:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說大星淡的支配力也不過如此嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.18,0:26:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多兩個月前  在最初與穩乃對局之時
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.68,0:26:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己就已經隱隱聽到了足音
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.02,0:26:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,與阿知賀的練習比賽第一天  衣和了三次海底撈月
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.15,0:26:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是其實是打算和五次的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.90,0:26:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.40,0:26:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天…  甚至連海底都沒能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.16,0:26:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼無精打采的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.25,0:26:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,憧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.33,0:26:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.33,0:26:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,補充糖分
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.17,0:26:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.55,0:26:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晴繪說這樣繼續下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.42,0:26:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.64,0:27:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.89,0:27:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還剩一次半莊嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.14,0:27:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…還剩十一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.98,0:27:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.65,0:27:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廣告播完啦  各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.07,0:27:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上到電視機前集合！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.90,0:27:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼不把廣告當回事的話  贊助商又要來抱怨了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.45,0:27:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身為正式解說員真是對不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.99,0:27:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是自由解說員也不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.95,0:27:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我被炒了的話  小健夜可要負起責任養我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.96,0:27:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…怎麼是我的責任？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.13,0:27:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才也全怪小鍛治雀士才跑題了！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.67,0:27:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.21,0:27:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來  大將戰終於將進入後半了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.97,0:27:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.22,0:27:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上決賽名額的戰鬥也進入了高潮！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.60,0:27:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的只有一回半莊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.77,0:27:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,賭上20個人的命運  最終之戰即將開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.91,0:28:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,龍華…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.29,0:28:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽——
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.25,0:28:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.12,0:28:24.17,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Image...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:28.35,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}加速して行く未来に
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.45,0:28:34.85,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}描いてく奇跡の形
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.99,0:28:40.05,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君と手を繋いでるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.13,0:28:46.62,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}諦めるなんてありえないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.77,0:28:51.85,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}手のひらには　戦いあって
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.98,0:28:57.73,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}積み重なった傷跡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.84,0:29:00.91,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}さぁ、いこう？旅をしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.01,0:29:09.33,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}銀河が残してきた記憶に新たなる一手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:16.07,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}こぼれ響く音がリズムになって　夢咲かせようと
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.17,0:29:21.67,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}フィールドを歌うわ　so futuristic player
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.74,0:29:24.83,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重なる想い　次の笑顔へ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.91,0:29:27.75,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}そう、確かな勝利へ
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.82,0:29:30.83,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}エールになるように　指を絡めるの
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.91,0:29:37.85,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}辿りついて　Over future
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.12,0:28:24.17,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}Image...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:28.35,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}寄宿在加速的未來中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.45,0:28:34.85,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}描繪出奇跡的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.99,0:28:40.05,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}雖然與你兩手相牽
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.13,0:28:46.62,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}也絕對無法放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.77,0:28:51.85,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}手心之中　奏響戰鬥的樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.98,0:28:57.73,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}喚醒經久積累的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.84,0:29:00.91,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那麼　出發前行吧？開始一段旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.01,0:29:09.33,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}為銀河之中殘留的記憶刻下嶄新的一式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:16.07,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}飄零的音聲交集成旋律　由我們來尋找夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.17,0:29:21.67,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}唱響起原野之歌　so futuristic player
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.74,0:29:24.83,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}重疊的思緒　匯作下次的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.91,0:29:27.75,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}是的　指引著那必然的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.82,0:29:30.83,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}十指緊扣　彼此聲援
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.91,0:29:37.85,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}終將抵達那　Over future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.62,0:29:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔哦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.44,0:29:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩  你怎麼了  為什麼突然跑起來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.35,0:29:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一回想起吉野山  我的身體就不由自主地…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.48,0:29:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.57,0:29:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小心那邊  往裏走是懸崖絕壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.62,0:29:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好危險！
